bio: I was born and raised in New York and have been a resident of the West Village for many years.  As the Office Manager, I help keep the Office running smoothly and oversees support services.  I enjoy working in creative environments and happy to be part of the Ennead team.  When I'm not working you’ll often find me in the kitchen cooking and exploring new recipes.
